title: Easy Listening mix 2
description:
FORMAT: mp3
QUALITY: 128 kbps or better

These are all hand picked soft tunes and ballads. This collection compliments the FIRST Easy Listening mix that I've uploaded, so be sure to combine the two. I've tried to add new tunes and dig up goldies. This is an ongoing process, so be sure to keep tuned for part 3 in a few months. Please post here any song suggestions that you feel I've left out!
